   <div class="lp-block lp-section lp-section--name-domains lp-section-domains lp-pb-48 lp-pb-120@M lp-pt-48 lp-pt-96@M is-style-gray-0-mono" style="background:#F6F7F7" data-section-name="domains">
    <div class="lp-section__content"> 
     <div class="lp-block lp-content lp-content--text-alignment lp-content--text-alignment-left lp-wrapper lp-wrapper--layout-left-ppppp"> 
      <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-huge-font-size">Claim your home on the web</h2> 
     </div> 
     <div class="lp-block lp-content lp-content--text-alignment lp-content--text-alignment-left lp-wrapper lp-wrapper--layout-left-p lp-pb-24"> 
      <p>Grab the perfect domain—with or without a website—for an unbeatable price. The popular .com, .org, and .net extensions start at just <span class="lp-product-price lp-product-price--domain_reg lp-product-price-options--hide-period-string lp-product-price-options--hide-null-decimals lp-product-price--is-loaded"><span class="lp-product-price__current-price">R$60</span></span> per year. Easy to remember, easy to share, and sure to stand out.</p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="lp-block lp-content lp-wrapper lp-wrapper--layout-wide"> 
      <div class="lp-block lp-form-typed"> 
       <form class="lp-block lp-form" action="https://wordpress.com/start/domain/domain-only/" method="GET" target="_blank">
        <div class="lp-form__content"> 
         <div class="lp-block lp-form-typed-field">
          <div class="lp-block lp-form-field">
           <input class="lp-form-field__content" type="search" name="new" required autocomplete="off" maxlength="60" autocapitalize="none">
          </div> 
          <div class="lp-block lp-typed" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true">
           <div class="lp-typed__content">
            <span class="lp-typed__content__indicator"></span>
           </div>
          </div> 
         </div> 
         <div class="lp-block lp-button lp-form-button lpc lpc-cta-domains">
          <button type="submit">Find your domain</button>
         </div> 
         <input type="hidden" name="search" value="yes">
        </div>
       </form> 
      </div> 
     </div> 
    </div>
   </div> 
   <div class="lp-block lp-section lp-section--name-hosting lp-section--has-background lp-section-hosting lp-pt-48 lp-pt-144@M lp-pb-48 lp-pb-120@M is-style-gray-90-mono" style="--lp-position-x:100%;--lp-position-y:-3%;background:#181c1f;--lp-size:fit" data-section-name="hosting">
    <div class="lp-section__background lp-section__background--has-image lp-section__background--name-image-full">
     <div class="lp-section__background-layer" style="background-image:url(https://s1.wp.com/wp-content/themes/h4/assets/hosting/globe.svg)"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="lp-section__content"> 
     <div class="lp-block lp-content lp-content--text-alignment lp-content--text-alignment-left lp-wrapper lp-wrapper--layout-wide"> 
      <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-huge-font-size">Host with the best</h2> 
     </div> 
     <div class="lp-block lp-content lp-content--text-alignment lp-content--text-alignment-left lp-wrapper lp-wrapper--layout-left lp-pb-30 lp-pb-12@M"> 
