        <div class="lp-image__content">
         <span class="lp-lazy-image" style="max-width:110px"><span class="lp-lazy-image__content" style="padding-top:calc(46/110*100%)"><img src="https://wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/vip-logo.webp" loading="lazy" alt="" role="presentation" width="110" height="46"></span></span>
        </div>
       </div> 
       <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-large-font-size">Think WordPress isn’t for the enterprise? Think&nbsp;again.</h2> 
       <p>What do Salesforce, Al Jazeera, Capgemini, and Facebook have in common?</p> 
       <p>They trust WordPress VIP—the enterprise platform built on WordPress—to deliver performance at scale while meeting the highest security standards. Starting at $25,000/year.<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://wpvip.com/wordpress-vip-agile-content-platform?utm_source=WordPresscom&amp;utm_medium=automattic_referral&amp;utm_campaign=lohp" target="_blank"></a></p> 
       <div class="lp-block lp-button lpc lpc-cta-vip"> 
        <div class="wp-block-button is-style-wide">
         <a class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button" href="https://wpvip.com/wordpress-vip-agile-content-platform?utm_source=WordPresscom&amp;utm_medium=automattic_referral&amp;utm_campaign=lohp">Get a demo</a>
        </div> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="lp-block lp-block--has-breakpoints lp-block--has-breakpoint-M lp-block--has-breakpoint-L lp-container" style="flex: 1.1; margin-right: -20px">
       <div class="lp-block lp-image">
